ip: , one this story concerning the person righteous/honest/sensible impasalerep of mangune-kune karereetan—migpatey the all his child, naawe the all wealth din, and miggingumaan pad indeed again he of mangune-kune dalu. And/Now due seven part of story of this document. And/Now by means of sika stories, impanengneng of writer ke what the inggeram of Hub and of me alukuy rin concerning the sika me karereetan. And/Now the important part of story, iyan that paahi of God of carrying of his people. And/Now nataman, migpapitew mismu the God ki Hub.

meta.ip: Te marani pad of first of this document, ingkahiyan of Satan the God of not good the carrying of his people egdasahan din the me righteous/honest/sensible. Therefore there egpangkus of iyan naan just reason doing of righteous/honest/sensible the people due to gift. And/Now kenad e from heart dan the making ran of righteous/honest/sensible. And/Now this indeed the said by Satan concerning Hub. Therefore intuhutan of God Satan eg-el-elehan the pegkamatinumanen of Hub ke continue-bulus naan pad he righteous/honest/sensible ke eg-antus he.

And/Now by means of karaan faith, impasabut of me alukuy of Hub mig-antus he due to because sinned he. But for ki Hub, not perem correct eg-antus he of sika punishment because righteous/honest/sensible ma he person. Ware din nasabut ke mania of intuhutan of God eggingumaan he of makaliyas-liyas dalu of righteous/honest/sensible ma he person. Therefore inhanggat din the God eggendiye them of hukumanan. And/Now minsan pad due, ware naawei the faith of Hub, but igkeupii rin eg-ileen he righteous/honest/sensible of God, and egkaangken din ded the kabantug isip righteous/honest/sensible person.

Ware tabaka of God the questions of Hub. But inggehet ded of God the faith of Hub, by means of power and wisdom/knowledge din. And/Now in-ila of Hub greatest matagseb the God, other of pegpariralem din, and migbuyu he of pasaylu of nenallalag din from langet din.

And/Now the final of this document, migpanengneng impalibed ded ki Hub the good keugpe din, and migsubla pad he matubung du of long ago. And/Now impangehetan of God the me alukuy of Hub, because ware ma them nakanengneng ke mania of mig-antus Hub. Hub just the nakasabut madmaresen pad the God du of karaan faith.
